get elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"f0888dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-952c4cd h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"952c4cd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CGB embodies the definition of a community<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fbf361c elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"fbf361c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd51703 parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cd51703\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>CGB is a \u201cNo Bully Zone\u201d. We live the philosophy and commitment of zero tolerance when it comes to bullying; a robust anti-bullying policy is stringently enforced. Our impressive success rate of restoring and mending temporarily damaged relationships is testament to our beliefs.<\/p><p>We care for ourselves and others. New parents and students are pleased to experience the warm and welcoming environment. Respect for each other, the broader community and the environment are central values. Through school-wide projects to promote sustainability and community service initiatives, students develop dispositions of empathy, service toward others, global citizenship and participation that will go beyond their school years.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-faf3744 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-stretch elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"faf3744\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f41158b animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"f41158b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46b8549 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"46b8549\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b0e7d4 h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1b0e7d4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The CGB family extends beyond the walls of our school<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4dc324d elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"4dc324d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b262091 parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b262091\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 21.3333px; text-align: left;\">We work with and learn from students and adults in many other schools, including those of the UNCOLI (Union Colegios Internacionales) and those of Round Square. We also work with schools located in less privileged areas of Bogota. &nbsp;At the heart of the IB Diploma Programme lies the philosophy of Creativity, Action and Service. A pro-active Parent Teacher Association works in partnership with the school to support meeting the needs of our school community. The committees serve not only to provide leadership opportunities for students; but also endeavour to make our community the best it can be.<\/span><br><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2cba72d animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"2cba72d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;background_ba